This is a program that I will use to execute a given command when there's action on the parallel port. More precisely the programm will take on parameter, the command it will execute. And since this is a program i need for a specific incident it will look for change in action on pin 13 on the parallel port.

The program will check for change in status on pin 13 all the time. If it notice a change in status it will execute the given command.
